Response Codes
The Hubtel Balance Query and Transfer API uses standard HTTP error reporting. Successful requests return HTTP status codes in the 2xx. Failed requests return status codes in 4xx and 5xx.

Response Codes are included in the JSON response body, which contains information about the error or status

HTTP Status Code	ResponseCode	Description	Required Action
200	0000/ 0001	The request has been processed successfully	None
401		None	Pass the correct account number in the request. Ensure your API keys are valid.
400	4000	Prepaid Deposit ID is invalid for this transaction./Provided client reference already exists. Please check and try again.	Ensure you are passing the correct Prepaid Deposit ID/ Ensure ClientReference is unique.